    "headline": "Zimmer Biomet Announces First Quarter 2026 Financial Results",
    "summary": "Zimmer Biomet Holdings, Inc. (NYSE and SIX: ZBH) today reported financial results for the quarter ended March 31, 2026. The Company reported first quarter net sales of $2.087 billion, an increase of 9.3% over the prior year period, an increase of 6.8% on a constant currency1 basis and an increase of 2.9% on an organic constant currency1 basis. Net earnings for the first quarter were $238.1 million, or $409.4 million on an adjusted1 basis.",
